data.description: Country living just minutes from town!! Cozy updated three-bedroom home on over two acres. Large garage complete with heater, air-conditioner, washer, dryer, generator hook-up, restroom, and an attached greenhouse. Mini barn complete with electricity. Pool, playset, and ample outdoor space perfect for entertaining. High speed internet available.  Septic genie in place. Covered front porch and enclosed carport surrounded by newer asphalt driveway.
